nd":"text","text":" Mercy triumphs over judgment."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jb 22:6","book":"Job","chapter":22,"verse":6},{"label":"Pr 21:13","book":"Pro","chapter":21,"verse":13},{"label":"Mt 5:7","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":7},{"label":"Mt 18:32–35","book":"Mat","chapter":18,"verse":32}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:2:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"What good is it, my brothers and sisters, if someone claims to have faith but does not have works? Can such faith save him?"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:2:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"If a brother or sister is without clothes and lacks daily food "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:2:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"and one of you says to them, “Go in peace, stay warm, and be well fed,” but you don’t give them what the body needs, what good is it? "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 25:35–36","book":"Mat","chapter":25,"verse":35,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 3:11","book":"Luk","chapter":3,"verse":11,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 3:16–18","book":"1Jn","chapter":3,"verse":16,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 25:35–36","book":"Mat","chapter":25,"verse":35},{"label":"Lk 3:11","book":"Luk","chapter":3,"verse":11},{"label":"1Jn 3:16–18","book":"1Jn","chapter":3,"verse":16}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:2:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"In the same way faith, if it does not have works, is dead by itself."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:2:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But someone will say, “You have faith, and I have works.” "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"The quotation may end here or after v. 18b or v. 19."},{"kind":"text","text":" Show me your faith without works, and I will show you faith by my works. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 3:28","book":"Rom","chapter":3,"verse":28,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 11:33","book":"Heb","chapter":11,"verse":33,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 3:13","book":"Jas","chapter":3,"verse":13,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 3:28","book":"Rom","chapter":3,"verse":28},{"label":"Heb 11:33","book":"Heb","chapter":11,"verse":33},{"label":"Jms 3:13","book":"Jas","chapter":3,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"The quotation may end here or after v. 18b or v. 19."}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:2:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You believe that God is one. Good! Even the demons believe —and they shudder. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 6:4","book":"Deu","chapter":6,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 8:29","book":"Mat","chapter":8,"verse":29,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 4:34","book":"Luk","chapter":4,"verse":34,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 6:4","book":"Deu","chapter":6,"verse":4},{"label":"Mt 8:29","book":"Mat","chapter":8,"verse":29},{"label":"Lk 4:34","book":"Luk","chapter":4,"verse":34}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:2:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Senseless person! Are you willing to learn that faith without works is useless? "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:2:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Wasn’t Abraham our father justified by works in offering Isaac his son on the altar? "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:2:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You see that faith was active together with his works, and by works, faith was made complete, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 22:9","book":"Gen","chapter":22,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 1:3","book":"1Th","chapter":1,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 11:17","book":"Heb","chapter":11,"verse":17,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 22:9","book":"Gen","chapter":22,"verse":9},{"label":"1Th 1:3","book":"1Th","chapter":1,"verse":3},{"label":"Heb 11:17","book":"Heb","chapter":11,"verse":17}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:2:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"and the Scripture was fulfilled that says, Abraham believed God, and it was credited to him as righteousness, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 15:6","book":"Gen","chapter":15,"verse":6,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 15:6","book":"Gen","chapter":15,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 4:3","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":3,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 3:6","book":"Gal","chapter":3,"verse":6,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" and he was called God’s friend. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Ch 20:7","book":"2Ch","chapter":20,"verse":7,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 41:8","book":"Isa","chapter":41,"verse":8,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 15:6","book":"Gen","chapter":15,"verse":6},{"label":"Gn 15:6","book":"Gen","chapter":15,"verse":6},{"label":"Rm 4:3","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":3},{"label":"Gl 3:6","book":"Gal","chapter":3,"verse":6},{"label":"2Ch 20:7","book":"2Ch","chapter":20,"verse":7},{"label":"Is 41:8","book":"Isa","chapter":41,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:2:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You see that a person is justified by works and not by faith alone. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:2:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"In the same way, wasn’t Rahab the prostitute also justified by works in receiving the messengers and sending them out by a different route? "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jos 2:4","book":"Jos","chapter":2,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jos 2:6","book":"Jos","chapter":2,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jos 2:15","book":"Jos","chapter":2,"verse":15,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 11:31","book":"Heb","chapter":11,"verse":31,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jos 2:4","book":"Jos","chapter":2,"verse":4},{"label":"Jos 2:6","book":"Jos","chapter":2,"verse":6},{"label":"Jos 2:15","book":"Jos","chapter":2,"verse":15},{"label":"Heb 11:31","book":"Heb","chapter":11,"verse":31}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:2:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For just as the body without the spirit is dead, so also faith without works is dead."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783099560865}